 FlavorVault  
#### Your personal vault for delicious recipes and food stories | April 2025  
#### By **Alex Cook, Jamie Patel**

## Description  
**FlavorVault** is a full-stack food web application that allows users to explore global recipes, save their favorite meals, and share their own food creations. It blends cooking with storytelling ‚Äî encouraging users to upload not just ingredients and instructions, but the story behind the dish.

With a clean interface and user-friendly navigation, FlavorVault is perfect for anyone who loves food, whether you're a casual home cook or a passionate foodie.

## Features  
- ü•ò Browse a growing collection of curated recipes  
- üìñ Submit your own recipes with rich stories and photos  
- ‚ù§Ô∏è Save and organize favorite recipes in personal collections  
- üîç Filter by cuisine, dietary preference, cooking time, and difficulty  
- üçé Nutritional info and tips included on every recipe page

