5. Open the app in your browser at `http://localhost:3000`

## Known Bugs  
- Image optimization on recipe upload may be slow on mobile  
- Social sharing preview cards may not load properly on some platforms  
- "Save Recipe" button requires login ‚Äî no feedback given if user is not logged in (UX fix planned)

## Technologies Used  
- Next.js (React Framework)  
- Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Storage)  
- Tailwind CSS  
- Cloudinary (image handling)  
- Spoonacular API (nutrition + extra recipes)  
- Markdown support for rich text recipe steps  

